<html>
<head>
    <title>Savings Box Anthology</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            align-items: center; 
            justify-content: center; 
            height: 100vh; 
            background: #282c34;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        h1 { 
            text-align: center; 
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            font-size: 36px; 
        }
        p { 
            max-width: 600px; 
            text-align: center; 
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            font-size: 18px; 
        }
        .button { 
            padding: 10px 20px; 
            background-color: #007BFF; 
            color: white; 
            border: none; 
            border-radius: 5px; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .button:hover { 
            background-color: #0056b3; 
        }
        .frosted-glass {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-cover" style="background-image: url(/game/preview.png); color: #fff; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
    <div class="frosted-glass">
        <h1>Savings Box Anthology</h1>
        <p>In Savings Box Anthology, you will embark on a thrilling adventure where you must navigate through various challenges and collect as many savings as possible. Use your skills to overcome obstacles and reach your financial goals!</p>
        <a href="/game/savingsbox.html" class="button">Play Savings Box</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
